_:N8b05f12baa4840e7ac72ee78e15a42d7 <http://schema.org/description> "We encourage fair and efficient arrangements in the workplace by resolving collective disputes in England, Scotland and Wales, either by voluntary agreement or, if necessary, through a legal decision. CAC is a tribunal of the Department for Business and Trade ." .
